### `AgentDefinition`

Configuration for a subagent defined programmatically.

```typescript theme={null}
type AgentDefinition = {
  description: string;
  tools?: string[];
  disallowedTools?: string[];
  prompt: string;
  model?: string;
  mcpServers?: AgentMcpServerSpec[];
  skills?: string[];
  initialPrompt?: string;
