### `SDKMessage`

Union type of all possible messages returned by the query.

```typescript theme={null}
type SDKMessage =
  | SDKAssistantMessage
  | SDKUserMessage
  | SDKUserMessageReplay
  | SDKResultMessage
  | SDKSystemMessage
  | SDKPartialAssistantMessage
  | SDKCompactBoundaryMessage
  | SDKStatusMessage
